cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and connection establishment issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FDM to an invalid value of 5 (valid values are 0-3) will cause PRACH configuration errors and uplink synchronization failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FDM 設定為無效值 5（有效值為 0-3）會導致 PRACH 配置錯誤和上行鏈路同步失敗。
